Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.80,0:32:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.35,0:32:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.15,0:32:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.11,0:32:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.57,0:32:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事 手拿開 寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.32,0:32:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手拿開
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.12,0:32:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我知道 寶貝 我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.33,0:32:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.37,0:32:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 來…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.75,0:32:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 寶貝 你沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.80,0:32:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道…寶貝 我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.88,0:33:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.97,0:33:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會沒事的 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.26,0:33:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶貝…聽我說
