Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.81,0:33:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.44,0:33:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湯米 幫幫我
