Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.88,0:37:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個小針頭
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.47,0:37:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.27,0:37:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.21,0:38:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.16,0:39:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十張
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.26,0:39:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有別的工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.18,0:39:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天沒有 明天有清掃街道
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.02,0:39:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或維護下水道
